y, The dinner and Queen on Pinterest |publisher=Pinterest.com |date= |accessdate=27 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pinterest.com/pin/470907704762221232/ |title=Crown princess victoria, Princess victoria and Queen on Pinterest |publisher=Pinterest.com |date= |accessdate=27 November 2016}}</ref>\n** Recipient of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Norway|King Olav V's Anniversary Medal 1957-1982]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n** Recipient of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Norway|King Haakon VII Centennial Medal]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n** Recipient of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Norway|Silver Jubilee Medal of King Harald V]]<ref>http://gpdhome.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c648253ef01bb08adc56b970d-pi</ref>\n* {{flag|Poland}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of the White Eagle (Poland)|Order of the White Eagle]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" />\n* {{flag|Portugal}}:\n** Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of Saint James of the Sword]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pinterest.com/pin/470907704763103757/ |title=The state, Tiaras and Portugal on Pinterest |publisher=Pinterest.com |date= |accessdate=27 November 2016}}</ref><ref name=portpres /><ref>http://ifokus-assets.se/53d24fefd9d021f4b2a7d0cce08751bf/shrink/700x/uploads/8a5/8a54304ee70e7c2fbcad12a916c9c2a8/1310013.jpg</ref>\n** Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of Prince Henry]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref name=portpres>{{cite web |publisher=Portuguese Presidency Website |title=Orders search form: type \"REI Carlos XVI\" in \"nome\", then click \"Pesquisar\" |url=http://www.ordens.presidencia.pt/?idc=154&list=1 |language=Portuguese |accessdate=16 October 2012}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Romania}}: Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of the Star of Romania]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kungahuset.se/royalcourt/royalfamily/latestnews/2008/2008/statevisitfromromania.5.edea36911759ad82de80006592.html |title=State visit from