als - Reservoir Photo |website=www.reservoirphoto.com |accessdate=29 May 2018 }}{{Dead link|date=October 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=\"reservoirphoto.com\"/>\n* {{flag|Germany}}: Grand Cross Special Class of the [[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theroyalforums.com/forums/f22/state-visit-from-germany-to-sweden-may-20-22-2003-a-366.html#post9806 |title=State visit of President Johannes Rau in Sweden in 2003 |publisher=theroyalforums.com |accessdate=19 August 2012}}{{unreliable source? |date=August 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cdn.theroyalforums.com/forums/attachment.php?attachmentid=6536&d=1053478212 |title=King's photo\n|accessdate=19 August 2012}}{{unreliable source? |date=August 2012}}</ref>\n** {{Flagicon|Saxe-Coburg-Gotha}} [[House of Saxe-Coburg and Gotha|Ducal Family of Saxe-Coburg and Gotha]]: Knight Grand Cross of the [[Saxe-Ernestine House Order|Ducal Royal Saxe-Ernestine Saxe-Coburg and Gotha House Order]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-IOzEjPj6KCU/UcDOWiGnUaI/AAAAAAAAEB4/qdO29jYEbZA/s1600/Screen+Shot+2013-06-18+at+1.57.11+PM.png |title=King Carl XVI Gustaf wearing the Grand Cross ribbon bar at the birthday of his cousin, Prince Andreas, Hereditary Duke of Saxe-Coburg and Gotha |date= |accessdate=27 November 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Greece}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Redeemer]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalcourt.se/kungafamiljen/aktuellahandelser/2008/2008arkiv/galamiddagpakungligaslottet.5.36df73941192994694f80005284.html |publisher=Royal Court of Sweden |title=Galamiddag p\u00e5 Kungliga slottet |language=Swedish |date=21 May 2008 |accessdate=19 August 2012}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Holy See}}: Knight with the Collar of the [[Order of Pope Pius IX]]<ref name=\"ListOfOrders\" />\n* {{flag|Hungary}}: Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of Merit of th